Title: Humanity!?
Narrative:
Horrific case reported from Delhi area is showing some minors mercilessly beating stray dogs. They have allegedly killed 40 dogs so far. The incident is a big question on Humanity.

My soul is literally crying after watching this..... Do something take strict action regarding this issue.... Animals only want love and affection from us in result we give them buckets of hate....
Why... Why... Why..
